Consider the linear system
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\{ \begin{array}{rcrcrlr}
x & + & y & - & z & = & -2\\
3x & - & 5y & + & 13z & = & 18\\
x & - & 2y & + & 5z & = & k
