\]

\end_inset

Thus,
 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{x}_{2}-\vec{x}_{1}$
\end_inset

 solves 
\begin_inset Formula $A\vec{x}=\vec{0}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

